      <div class="msgContentFrame">Sounds about right to me, although if I had to guess piety is probably needed for all the crafts and is not GS specific.  Since items that goldsmith's make benefit both melee and magic classes, it would seem fair that the stats needed to be successful mix a melee stat (dex) with a magic stat (int).</div>
