      <div class="msgContentFrame">I was wondering this same thing, as I'm sure many players testing crafting are doing at the moment. <br /> <br />If you look at the Point Allotment screen there are lined up as such: <br /><b> <br />Strength    : Fire <br />Vitality    : Water <br />Dexterity   : Lightning <br />Mind        : Wind <br />Intelligence: Earth <br />Piety       : Ice</b> <br /> <br />If this is a hint as to which physical attributes align with which respective elemental attributes, then it's possible to imagine that whatever crystals/shards you tend to use the most of for any given synth, you probably want more points in that respective physical attribute as well(ie, your synths tend to be wind and lightning shards, you want more points in Dex and Mind). <br /> <br />However, this has no basis in reality.  I'm just blowing hot air out my azz.  It's the only kinda air that comes outta there =D</div>
